when you're an aristocrat.

563
00:38:42,278 --> 00:38:43,154
How smug of you.

564
00:38:43,237 --> 00:38:45,239
-Aristocrat.
-Potential Jung Hye-jeong.

565
00:38:46,032 --> 00:38:47,616
Being treated like this

566
