773
01:00:32,754 --> 01:00:33,713
What?

774
01:00:34,714 --> 01:00:37,800
Don't think about whether
your love will last a day or forever.

775
01:00:37,967 --> 01:00:39,969
Even if your heart is ready
to last forever,

776
01:00:40,053 --> 01:00:42,096
humans are mortal beings.

777
01:00:42,347 --> 01:00:45,516
