780
01:00:48,936 --> 01:00:50,980
Are you saying she plagiarized mine?

781
01:00:51,064 --> 01:00:53,441
Ms. Lim plagiarized yours? No way.

782
01:00:53,524 --> 01:00:54,525
Hey!

783
01:00:54,984 --> 01:00:57,528
Did you bring me here
so I can't yell at you?

784
01:00:57,654 --> 01:00:58,863
That's one reason.

785
01:00:59,364 --> 01:01:01,240
I'm just caught in the trap

786
01:01:01,324 --> 01:01:04,243
that I've worked on
so passionately for seven years.

787
01:01:04,327 --> 01:01:05,578
Your script was really fun to read.

788
01:01:05,662 --> 01:01:08,331
We just borrowed
a few words from our diary.

789
01:01:08,456 --> 01:01:12,502
Filming the memories of you and Ms. Lim
would make me feel jealous, won't it?

790
01:01:12,585 --> 01:01:14,337
Do you like Jin-joo?

791
01:01:14,420 --> 01:01:16,881
You didn't call her Ms. Lim. "Jin-joo"?

792
01:01:16,964 --> 01:01:19,175
